  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Power cut for 3 hours and 40 minutes",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Janaka Ratnayake, chairman of the Public Utilities Commission, said today (19) afternoon that due to the lack of sufficient fuel and water for power generation, the power cut was allowed to be extended to 3 hours and 40 minutes tomorrow (20).",
        "Accordingly, Mr. Ratnayake said that electricity will be cut for 2 hours and 20 minutes during the day and 2 hours and 20 minutes during the night in the 20 zones from 'A' to 'W'.",
        "2 hours and 30 minutes for the 'CC' category, which also includes Colombo cities, from 6.00 am to 8.30 am, and 3 hours from 5.00 am to 8.00 am for M, N, O, X, Y and Z zones. Mr. Janaka Ratnayake, chairman of the Public Utilities Commission, further said that it was given."
      ],
